@startuml Motion Service - Détaillé (Remplace MetaManager)

!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

class MotionService {
  - _stage_manager: StageManager
  - _position_listeners: List[Callable]
  - _homing_status: Dict[str, bool]
  
  ' === Commandes de mouvement (ex-MetaManager) ===
  + move_to(axis: str, target_cm: float) -> bool
  + move_to_position(x_cm: float, y_cm: float) -> bool
  + home_axis(axis: str) -> bool
  + home_both_axes() -> bool
  + home_both_axes_blocking() -> bool
  + stop_axis(axis: str, immediate: bool) -> bool
  + emergency_stop_all() -> bool
  
  ' === Configuration vitesse (ex-MetaManager) ===
  + set_axis_speed_params(axis: str, params: SpeedParams) -> bool
  + get_axis_speed_params(axis: str) -> SpeedParams
  + apply_speed_configuration(config: SpeedConfig) -> bool
  
  ' === Requêtes d'état ===
  + get_current_position() -> Position
  + is_axis_homed(axis: str) -> bool
  + is_moving() -> bool
  + get_axis_limits() -> AxisLimits
  
  ' === Observateurs (remplace signaux Qt MetaManager) ===
  + subscribe_position_updates(callback: Callable) -> None
  + unsubscribe_position_updates(callback: Callable) -> None
  
  ' === Méthodes internes ===
  - _validate_position(x: float, y: float) -> bool
  - _convert_cm_to_inc(value_cm: float) -> int
  - _convert_inc_to_cm(value_inc: int) -> float
  - _on_position_changed(x_inc: int, y_inc: int) -> None
  - _on_homing_completed(axis: str) -> None
}

class Position {
  + x_cm: float
  + y_cm: float
  + timestamp: datetime
}

class SpeedParams {
  + low_speed: int
  + high_speed: int
  + acceleration: int
  + deceleration: int
}

class SpeedConfig {
  + x_params: SpeedParams
  + y_params: SpeedParams
}

class AxisLimits {
  + x_min_cm: float
  + x_max_cm: float
  + y_min_cm: float
  + y_max_cm: float
}

' === Relations avec GUI ===
class "EFImagingBench_GUI" as GUI {
  + move_to(axis)
  + home(axis)
  + stop(axis)
  + apply_speed_parameters()
}

' === Relations avec Domain (DIRECT) ===
class StageManager {
  + add_command_to_queue(cmd)
  + get_current_position()
  + get_axis_homed_status(axis)
  + set_axis_params(axis, params)
  + get_axis_params(axis) -> dict
  --
  <<signal>> position_changed
  <<signal>> status_changed
  <<signal>> error_occurred
}

' === Legacy (À supprimer) ===
class MetaManager <<deprecated>> {
  + move_to(axis, target_inc)
  + home_lock(axis)
  + home_both_lock()
  + stop(axis, immediate)
  + set_axis_params(axis, params)
  --
  <<À REMPLACER par MotionService>>
}

' === Relations ===
GUI --> MotionService : "utilise (nouveau)"
GUI ..> MetaManager : "<<legacy>> à migrer"

MotionService --> StageManager : "communication directe"
MetaManager ..> StageManager : "<<legacy>>"

MotionService ..> Position : "retourne"
MotionService ..> SpeedParams : "utilise"
MotionService ..> SpeedConfig : "utilise"
MotionService ..> AxisLimits : "retourne"

StageManager --> MotionService : "<<signal>> position_changed"

note right of MotionService
  **Remplace MetaManager pour le mouvement**
  
  **Responsabilités:**
  - Validation des positions (limites)
  - Conversion cm ↔ inc
  - Gestion observateurs position
  - API mouvement simplifiée
  - Vérification homing avant move
  
  **Migration depuis MetaManager:**
  - move_to() → MotionService.move_to()
  - home_lock() → MotionService.home_axis()
  - home_both_lock() → MotionService.home_both_axes_blocking()
  - stop() → MotionService.stop_axis()
  - set_axis_params() → MotionService.set_axis_speed_params()
  
  **Principe:**
  - Communication DIRECTE avec StageManager
  - Pas de couche intermédiaire
  - Responsabilité unique (SRP)
end note

note bottom of StageManager
  **StageManager (inchangé)**
  - Gestion threads/queues
  - Communication série
  - Buffer de positions
  - Signaux Qt
  
  Maintenant utilisé DIRECTEMENT
  par MotionService (plus de MetaManager)
end note

